This paper discusses face detection algorithms in the mobile domain, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses deep learning techniques and network architectures, which are topics related to machine learning (cs.MM) and deep learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the robustness of the proposed algorithms to occlusion, which is a topic related to computer security (cs.CR) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
